CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 15, 1956, pg. 14, reads: "'Youth Day' - Participants on the program at Mount Ararat Baptist Church were, front, left to right: Earl Smith, Audrey Ficklin, the Rev. C. A. Burrell, Betty Coles, Elizabeth Brown and Robert Russell. Back row: David Johnson, Nadine Poindexter, Marion Brown and Betty Jones. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Earl Smith, Audrey Ficklin, Rev. C. A. Burrell, Betty Coles, Elizabeth Brown, Robert Russell; back row: David Johnson, Nadine Poindexter, Marion Brown, and Betty Jones, posed in Mr. Ararat Baptist Church
